{"tid":929843,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗性交過程粗魯 冇戴安全套","createTime":"2018-12-06T01:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T04:16:41.000Z","uid":157545,"like":463,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"20efdb0e06ce6f8e7d8cf0c7f064b19eb100d406","tid":929843,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20181205/photo/bkn-20181205150008939-1205_00882_001_01b.jpg?20181205160012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20181205%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181205150008939-1205_00882_001_01b.jpg%3F20181205160012&h=733bd17f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葡萄牙球王C朗涉嫌2009年，喺美國拉斯維加斯強姦女子Kathryn Mayorga，最近流出佢當年同律師對話紀錄，呢位祖雲達斯射手當時辯稱，係女方主動挑逗佢，包括握實佢嘅下體，並擺出願意性交嘅姿勢。<br />\n<br />\n根據文件紀錄，C朗同律師講：「佢(Kathryn Mayorga)話第1次見面，都係唔好上床，但佢當時又用手捉住我下體。之後佢瞓喺床上面，我就由後面進入，我哋冇轉換姿勢，大約5至7分鐘，可能我捉住佢嗰陣令佢有瘀傷，所以佢話唔想要。」<br />\n<br />\nC朗仲透露，當時冇用安全套，所以冇喺Kathryn Mayorga身體內射精，而係射喺身體外面同毛毯上，最令人噁心係C朗用口水當做潤滑劑。<br />\n<br />\nC朗喺10月公開聲稱，自己冇強姦Kathryn Mayorga，所有指控都係謊言，更反指有人想借用佢嘅名氣做宣傳，事件不斷發酵之下，C朗仲有排煩。"},{"pid":"5821f305aea4852f1d71cb4a3a117edc5263ccb6","tid":929843,"uid":33907,"like":178,"dislike":2,"score":176,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 握實"},{"pid":"3cd25aa3f51006dcbffa72787771d6d73b044ecd","tid":929843,"uid":7790,"like":812,"dislike":5,"score":807,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:13:11.000Z","msg":"牙朗咁撚勇唔戴套"},{"pid":"0a4a0e6fe53c6380a1ea88b47d4cd98841d4789d","tid":929843,"uid":170365,"like":370,"dislike":5,"score":365,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:14:33.000Z","msg":"愛滋朗"},{"pid":"27740b53f60402e6fd5c74ab3ad6459f81402030","t